_Corbray\" title=\"House Corbray\">Corbray</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Elesham\" title=\"House Elesham\">Elesham</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Grafton\" title=\"House Grafton\">Grafton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hunter\" title=\"House Hunter\">Hunter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lynderly\" title=\"House Lynderly\">Lynderly</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Longthorpe\" title=\"House Longthorpe\">Longthorpe</a><sup>1</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Pryor\" title=\"House Pryor\">Pryor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Redfort\" title=\"House Redfort\">Redfort</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Royce\" title=\"House Royce\">Royce</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Ruthermont\" title=\"House Ruthermont\">Ruthermont</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Sunderland\" title=\"House Sunderland\">Sunderland</a><sup>1</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tollett\" title=\"House Tollett\">Tollett</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Torrent\" title=\"House Torrent\">Torrent</a><sup>1</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Waynwood\" title=\"House Waynwood\">Waynwood</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Knightly Houses</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hardyng\" title=\"House Hardyng\">Hardyng</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Shett_of_Gull_Tower\" title=\"House Shett of Gull Tower\">Shett of Gull Tower</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Shett_of_Gulltown\" title=\"House Shett of Gulltown\">Shett of Gulltown</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Templeton\" title=\"House Templeton\">Templeton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Waxley\" title=\"House Waxley\">Waxley</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/in